          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            202.66798400878906,
            282.7572937011719,
            250.38003540039062
          ],
          "text": "The Chairman and Managing Director / Chief Executive Officers, All Banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            266.1479797363281,
            172.7159881591797,
            282.1200256347656
          ],
          "text": "Madam / Dear Sir,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            297.80401611328125,
            536.0759887695312,
            330.4320373535156
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) based on performance in rendering customer service to the members of public",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            345.5279846191406,
            552.3411254882812,
            440.8199462890625
          ],
          "text": "In terms of the Preamble and under Section 45 of the RBI Act, 1934, and 35 A of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949, the Bank issues guidelines / instructions for realising the objectives of our Clean Note Policy. With a view to sustain these objectives, the Bank has formulated a scheme of incentives titled Currency Distribution and Exchange Scheme (CDES) in order to ensure that all bank branches provide better customer services to member of public.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99999237060547,
            461.447998046875,
            549.0157470703125,
            509.15997314453125
          ],
          "text": "2.\nThe Master Direction enclosed incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the subject. The Direction will be updated from time to time as and when fresh instructions are issued.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            529.66796875,
            492.8160095214844,
            545.6400146484375
          ],
          "text": "3.\nThis Master Direction has been placed on RBI website at www.rbi.org.in.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            571.0679931640625,
            157.416015625,
            587.0400390625
          ],
          "text": "Yours faithfully,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99998474121094,
            633.2279663085938,
            200.135986328125,
            665.0400390625
          ],
          "text": "(P. Vijaya Kumar) Chief General Manager",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
