      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            89.42401123046875,
            552.3359985351562,
            119.9520034790039
          ],
          "text": "Annex",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            90.0,
            127.10400390625,
            194.67601013183594,
            143.83200073242188
          ],
          "text": "1. Introduction -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            152.90399169921875,
            552.3411254882812,
            216.60006713867188
          ],
          "text": "The Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) for bank branches including currency chests has been formulated in order to ensure that all bank branches provide better customer service to members of public with regard to exchange of notes and coins, in keeping with the objectives of Clean Note Policy.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            90.0,
            226.404052734375,
            173.37600708007812,
            243.13204956054688
          ],
          "text": "2. Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00000762939453,
            252.34803771972656,
            552.3421020507812,
            284.2200622558594
          ],
          "text": "As per the scheme, banks are eligible for the following financial incentives for providing facilities for exchange of notes and coins:",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            80.27999877929688,
            296.4840087890625,
            102.93599700927734,
            327.0119934082031
          ],
          "text": "Sr.\nNo.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            157.8000030517578,
            296.4840087890625,
            493.2359924316406,
            313.2120056152344
          ],
          "text": "Nature of Service Particulars of Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            315.0,
            334.583984375,
            537.937255859375,
            351.3119812011719
          ],
          "text": "a. Capital Cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            86.58000183105469,
            334.6679992675781,
            299.0173034667969,
            398.2799987792969
          ],
          "text": "i) Opening of and maintaining currency chests at centers having population of less than 1 lakh in under banked States",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            315.0,
            350.5679931640625,
            537.9385986328125,
            476.77197265625
          ],
          "text": "50% of capital expenditure subject to a ceiling of ` 50 lakh per currency chest. In the North Eastern region up to 100% of capital expenditure is eligible for reimbursement subject to the ceiling of ` 50 lakh.\n\nb. Revenue cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            337.5,
            476.0880126953125,
            537.9373779296875,
            555.5400390625
          ],
          "text": "50% of revenue expenditure for the first 3 years. In the North Eastern region 50% of revenue expenditure will be reimbursed for the first 5 years.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            329.82000732421875,
            565.823974609375,
            523.057373046875,
            613.97998046875
          ],
          "text": "a. Exchange of soiled notes - ` 2 per packet for exchange of soiled notes up to denomination ` 50",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            85.26000213623047,
            565.8479614257812,
            297.9384765625,
            629.52001953125
          ],
          "text": "ii) Exchange of soiled notes/ adjudication of mutilated banknotes over the counter at bank branches",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            329.82000732421875,
            624.0239868164062,
            523.0562133789062,
            656.6520385742188
          ],
          "text": "b.\nAdjudication of mutilated notes - ` 2 per piece",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
