          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            87.7679672241211,
            537.9384155273438,
            133.37997436523438
          ],
          "text": "over the counter.\n\nii. The incentives would be paid on the",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            321.6000061035156,
            133.30799865722656,
            537.9373779296875,
            181.01998901367188
          ],
          "text": "basis of withdrawal from currency chest, without waiting for claims from banks.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            198.8279571533203,
            537.9395751953125,
            214.79995727539062
          ],
          "text": "iii. Banks may put in place a system of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            214.7279815673828,
            537.9397583007812,
            292.0799865722656
          ],
          "text": "checks and balances to ensure that coins are distributed to retail customers in small lots and not to bulk customers.\n\niv. The distribution of coins shall be",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            83.58000183105469,
            292.0080261230469,
            537.9384765625,
            403.67999267578125
          ],
          "text": "verified by RBI Regional Offices through inspection of currency chest / incognito visits to branches etc.\n\niv) Installation of Machines which extend cash related retail services to the public like -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            355.9679870605469,
            537.9362182617188,
            435.41998291015625
          ],
          "text": "The maximum amount of reimbursement for the machines will be as follows -\n\nFor Metro / Urban areas -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            136.67999267578125,
            413.5679931640625,
            300.57598876953125,
            477.17999267578125
          ],
          "text": "1. Cash Recyclers;\n2. ATMs dispensing lower denomination notes (i.e.\nup to denomination ` 100)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            435.2879943847656,
            537.9373779296875,
            610.9200439453125
          ],
          "text": "1. Cash Recyclers - 50% of the actual cost of the machine or ` 2,00,000 whichever is lower\n\n2. ATMs dispensing lower denomination notes (up to denomination ` 100) - 50% of the actual cost of the machine or ` 2,00,000 whichever is lower\n\nFor Semi-urban / Rural areas -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
