            610.7879638671875,
            537.9373779296875,
            754.6799926757812
          ],
          "text": "1. Cash Recyclers - 60% of the actual cost of the machine or ` 2,50,000 whichever is lower\n\n2. ATMs dispensing lower denomination notes (up to denomination ` 100) - 60% of the actual cost of the machine or ` 2,50,000 whichever is lower",
