            552.3384399414062,
            269.8800354003906
          ],
          "text": "ii) Similarly, incentive will be paid in respect of the adjudicated notes received along with the soiled note remittances / sent separately by registered / insured post in a sealed cover to the RBI. No separate claim is required to be made.",
          "font_info": {
