          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            305.6280212402344,
            552.341064453125,
            385.0799865722656
          ],
          "text": "i) The banks intending to purchase various machines as also establish currency chests during the period from July 01st to June 30th of a year, may submit their Annual Plans containing the details of the machines and the cost, to our Issue Offices latest by April 15 of every year on an ongoing basis. Our Issue offices, on receipt of the plans, may advise the maximum amount of reimbursement permissible to each bank for that year.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
